short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get to whatever you want by just typing.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Just Type is a quicker way to get to where you want to be. You define a list of actions for your favorite locations on the internet, and then you can search through them in the omnibox to jump to exactly where you want to be.

This is still in testing.
